snippet.textDisplay:
Its absurd to label yourself a climate activist at 17 years old. Just deplorable in my opinion. I have no beef with letting them join your crew for the passage, but if time is allotted to let these misinformed fear mongers promote their message I’m done with this channel.

Everyone should be doing all they can in their daily lives to reduce their carbon footprint, but manmade climate change is one of the biggest lies being spread in the media right now. Deforestation, pollution, obesity, all are 1000x more important to combat than the myth that debatable changes in the earth’s climate are due to minute elevations in co2 levels.

I do applaud Greta for eating a sustainable diet and promoting the health of the earth. Cheers to her on that one.
